### ============================================================
### 设置管理接口
### ============================================================

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken =

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 获取所有设置
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 更新设置
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storage_mode": "full",
  "truncate_length": "102400",
  "retention_days": "30",
  "store_sidecar_json": "false"
}
